SUMMARY: Séance: The Board Awakens
DESCRIPTION:Constellation Stage & Screen presents "Séance: The Board Awak
 ens"\, on stage January 29 - February 15\, 2026 at the Waldron Auditorium
 .\n\nSummon the Unknown.\n\nDare to uncover the terrifying secrets of the
  Ouija board in this spine-chilling theatrical experience. As the magic-f
 illed séance begins\, you’ll find yourself surrounded by the eerie remnan
 ts of the original Ouija board factory—still haunted by the untimely deat
 h of its inventor in 1927. As the spirits awaken\, will you unlock the da
 rk secrets of the past or become trapped in their world forever?\n\nStarr
 ing Rob Zabrecky\, two-time Stage Magician of the Year and resident séanc
 e specialist for the Magic Castle.\n\nRecommended for ages 13+.\n\nSee Co
 nstellation’s website for more information\, including a detailed perform
 ance schedule. Single tickets available starting on July 2\, 2025.\n\nLea
 rn more and find tickets at Constellation • Séance: The Board Awakens htt
 ps://seeconstellation.org/mainstage/seance/
CATEGORIES:Theatre,Visual-Arts
