SUMMARY: After the Storm presents "Constellations"
DESCRIPTION:What happens when a beekeeper and a cosmologist meet at a BBQ
 ? It sounds like the setup for a joke\, but instead it's the opening of a
  powerful story of love\, loss\, finding and losing love\, and facing the
  hardest paths together. Told through varying timelines\, audiences will 
 follow Roland (Bill Goveia) and Marianne (Emily Bedwell) from first dates
  to heartbreak to reconnection and beyond.\n\nAfter the Storm Productions
  is Bloomington's newest theater company. We are focused on using theater
  as a means for facing and exploring trauma.
CATEGORIES:Theatre
