  for IU Sing A Cappella 2026 on Saturday February 28th! IU Sing A Cappell
 a will showcase talented student groups performing for the opportunity to
  sing at the 2026 Little 500 races. IU Sing is a campus musical competiti
 on that\, for more than 80 years\, has gathered student groups to create 
 and perform original productions. With its rich history of hosting studen
 t events\, IUSF is proud to revive this time-honored IU tradition for a n
 ew generation.\n\nFunds raised from IU Sing will benefit the 2026 Student
 s Helping Students campaign.
