SUMMARY: The Forsytes Season 1\, Episode 1 | Additional Films and Guests
DESCRIPTION:Desire\, ambition\, and betrayal simmer in The Forsytes\, a l
 ush new period drama from Poldark writer Debbie Horsfield. Set within a w
 ealthy Victorian stockbroking family\, the series explores generational c
 lashes over tradition\, duty\, and the pursuit of love. Inspired by John 
 Galsworthy’s Forsyte Saga novels\, the story unfolds in the years before 
 the original books\, revealing lives shaped by loyalty\, sacrifice\, and 
 desire. See episode one before it premieres on PBS on March 22. [60 min\;
  drama\, romance\; English]
