SUMMARY: The DaVinci Code- Live on Stage
DESCRIPTION:Constellation Stage & Screen presents “The DaVinci Code\,” on
  stage March 26 - April 12 at the Waldron Auditorium.\n\nDan Brown’s inte
 rnational best-seller comes to life on stage in this thrilling\, high-sta
 kes adventure! When the curator of the Louvre is found murdered under mys
 terious circumstances\, symbologist Robert Langdon and cryptologist Sophi
 e Neveu are thrust into an investigation that quickly unravels into a dea
 dly conspiracy. As they follow a trail of cryptic puzzles and ancient cod
 es\, they discover a secret that could change the course of history. Pack
 ed with pulse-pounding suspense and stunning visuals\, The Da Vinci Code 
 is an exhilarating journey into the unknown.\n\n\nSee Constellation’s web
 site for more information\, including a detailed performance schedule. Le
 arn more and find tickets at seeconstellation.org/mainstage/da-vinci-code
 / https://seeconstellation.org/mainstage/da-vinci-code/ https://seeconste
 llation.org/mainstage/da-vinci-code/
