SUMMARY: ABRA Cadabra
DESCRIPTION:Attention all ABBA fans! Get ready for a night of glittering 
 costumes\, irresistible melodies\, and pure joy when ABRA Cadabra – the i
 nternationally acclaimed ABBA tribute band – takes the stage at Burkirk-C
 humley Theater in Bloomington on April 19\, 2026 @ 7:30pm.\n\nFor 25 year
 s\, ABRA Cadabra has been captivating audiences across the globe with fai
 thful yet fresh performances of ABBA’s timeless hits. From “Dancing Queen
 ” to “Mamma Mia” and “Take a Chance on Me\,” the band blends meticulous m
 usical detail with colorful visuals and an atmosphere designed to get aud
 iences on their feet.\n\nThe result is a high-energy\, family-friendly sp
 ectacle featuring a live band\, dancers\, dazzling costumes\, and multipl
 e wardrobe changes. Audiences are encouraged to sing\, clap\, and dance a
 long\, creating a shared moment of nostalgia and celebration.\n\nConnect 
 with ABRA Cadabra on Facebook & Instagram @ATributeToABBA and online at h
 ttp://www.iloveabba.com http://www.iloveabba.com/ www.iloveabba.com\n\nHe
 re’s what our fans are saying.\n\n“Best show we’ve ever seen!” – Gilberte
  Nowlan – Moncton\, NB\n\n“I’ve seen tributes to ABBA before\, they were 
 great\, but you are the best. If you come back East we will be there!” –J
 ack Hayward – Fredericton\, NB\n\n“Just saw your show in Regina. WOW! You
  guys are amazing – I took my (80+) mom and she loved it! The entire grou
 p is stunning\, never seen any performers acknowledge their entire crew\,
  go into the audience and so obviously love what you do! Thank you…we wil
 l come again!” – Rhonda Lamb – Regina\, SK
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,In-Person,Live,Music
X-TKF-FEATURED-IMAGE:https://d3flpus5evl89n.cloudfront.net/62fb9509b27fd5
 06428328ed/6974f6512c97af2cfcb6e207/scaled_1024.jpg
