SUMMARY: The Lunchbox Project with Reimagining Opera for Kids
DESCRIPTION:This year Reimagining Opera for Kids is excited to present Th
 e Lunchbox Project. Join our cast as they come together for lunch and exp
 lore all the different foods and cultures on display. Featuring music fro
 m six different contemporary composers\, The Lunchbox Project celebrates 
 diversity through different styles of music and food! This show is perfec
 t for elementary age audiences and audiences love the variety\, pacing\, 
 and audience interaction. Join us for this free event!\n\n
CATEGORIES:opera,Bloomington,Free,Music
