DESCRIPTION:Join us for the legendary IU Soul Revue’s annual spring conce
 rt! Get ready to groove as the music takes you on a journey through the b
 est of funk\, soul\, and R&B. Under the direction of Professor James Stro
 ng\, the IU Soul Revue is set to deliver a powerhouse performance that wi
 ll have the audience on their feet. This show promises to honor its rich 
 legacy in unforgettable fashion. Don’t miss it!
