SUMMARY: BEAT Spring Show
DESCRIPTION:Bloomington Expressive Arts Training: BEAT will present their
  14th annual BEAT Spring Show on Monday\, April 27th at 7pm at the Buskir
 k Chumley Theater. BEAT is a pre-professional\, community show choir prog
 ram for children grades 1-12 throughout Bloomington and surrounding areas
 . Come watch the members of Mini Sync\, Syncopation\, Amplitude AND our b
 rand new adult group\, Tempo\, sing and dance their HEARTS out! BEAT invi
 tes you to partake in this innovative\, engaging entertainment fit for th
 e whole family!! Come get to know these incredibly talented young people!
 !!\n\nSales start March 4th at noon! Children need a ticket of their own 
 unless they sit in a parent’s lap the duration of the show. There will be
  a 15 minute intermission.
